        public void setDontDisturbEnable(boolean enable)
        You can use don't disturb setting when you don't want to be disturbed by sedentary alert. Don't disturb time fixed to 12:00-2:00.In general this is the lunch break time.
        参数:
        enable - True for enable. False for disable.
